,\\\"$undefined\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Home to UNC, Chapel Hill offers a vibrant, walkable community for dogs. From the trails of Bolin Creek to the energy of Franklin Street, there is a youthful and active spirit here.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Chapel Hill, famously known as the \\\\\\\"Southern Part of Heaven,\\\\\\\" extends its welcoming atmosphere to our four-legged friends. Dominated by the University of North Carolina, the town has a vibrant, pedestrian-friendly energy that makes dog walking a delight. \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.visitchapelhill.org\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Franklin Street\\\"}],null,\\\", the cultural hub, is lined with businesses that often put out water bowls, and many restaurant patios are happy to host well-behaved dogs. It is the perfect place for social pups who enjoy the hustle and bustle of a college town environment, provided they are comfortable with crowds and new faces.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Away from the downtown buzz, Chapel Hill offers serene escapes into nature. The Bolin Creek Trail is a local treasure, providing a paved, shaded route that follows the creek bed, offering a cool retreat even in the humid summer months. For off-leash time, Homestead Park and Southern Community Park provide \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"excellent, fenced facilities\\\"}],null,\\\" where dogs can run freely. The town’s topography—rolling hills and wooded lots—makes for interesting and active walks just about anywhere you go. With a community that deeply values outdoor recreation and green space, Chapel Hill creates a harmonious balance between urban walkability and natural retreat.\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta primary\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"park-directory\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-list-check\\\"}],\\\"Browse directory\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta ghost\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"map-and-neighborhoods\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-geo-alt\\\"}],\\\"Open map\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/list-your-park\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta text-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-plus-circle\\\"}],\\\"Submit a park\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-footnotes\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",\\\"Homestead Park\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-sparkles\\\"}],\\\" \\\",\\\"Homestead Park\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",\\\"Bolin Creek Trail\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L31\\\",\\\" \\\",\\\"Bolin Creek Trail\\\"]}],\\\"$L32\\\"]}]]}],\\\"$L33\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L34\\\",\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"