ions.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is Franklin Street dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, many outdoor patios along Franklin Street welcome dogs. It’s a vibrant area for a walk, especially when the university is in session, but it can get crowded.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there leash laws in Chapel Hill?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Chapel Hill and Orange County strictly enforce leash laws. Dogs must be under control at all times, which usually means on a leash unless in a designated area.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can dogs hike at Occoneechee Mountain?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Nearby in Hillsborough, Occoneechee Mountain State Natural Area welcomes leashed dogs on its trails, offering some of the best views in the region.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Chapel Hill\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Chapel Hill\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Southern Part of Heaven\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Chapel Hill Canines\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-chip-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Dog Parks\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"2\"}],\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Trail Miles\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"15+\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Home to UNC, Chapel Hill offers a vibrant, walkable community for dogs. From the trails of Bolin Creek to the energy of Franklin Street, there is a youthful and active spirit here.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Chapel Hill, famously known as the \\\"Southern Part of Heaven,\\\" extends its welcoming atmosphere to our four-legged friends. Dominated by the University of North Carolina, the town has a vibrant, pedestrian-friendly energy that makes dog walking a delight. \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.visitchapelhill.org\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Franklin Street\"}],null,\", the cultural hub, is lined with businesses that often put out water bowls, and many restaurant patios are happy to host well-behaved dogs. It is the perfect place for social pups who enjoy the hustle and bustle of a college town environment, provided they are comfortable with crowds and new faces.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Away from the downtown buzz, Chapel Hill offers serene escapes into nature. The Bolin Creek Trail is a local treasure, providing a paved, shaded route that follows the creek bed, offering a cool retreat even in the humid summer months. For off-leash time, Homestead Park and Southern Community Park provide \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"excellent, fenced facilities\"}],null,\" where dogs can run freely. The town’s topography—rolling hills and wooded lots—makes for interesting and active walks just about anywhere you go. With a community that deeply values outdoor recreation and green space, Chapel Hill creates a harmonious balance between urban walkability and natural retreat.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Homestead Park\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Homestead Park\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Bolin Creek Trail\",{\"children\":[\"$L31\",\" \",\"Bolin Creek Trail\"]}],\"$L32\"]}]]}],\"$L33\"]}]}],\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$undefined\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\",\"$L3e\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"children\":\"About us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"